OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain becoming heavy and persistent in
OL,8,Fthe west, especially Skye Wester Ross
OL,9,Fand Lochaber with localised flooding
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudy with occasional rain,
OL,13,Fmore persistent and occasionally heavy
OL,14,Fin northwest Best of any drier and
OL,15,Fbrighter spells in the east towards
OL,16,FInverness, where warmer. Quite windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
